					<h4>Part 2: Oregon, Wyoming, and Other Western States</h4>
		
		<h1>Best in the West Part II: Favorite Books of The Year</h1>
		<h2><i></i></h2>
		<div class="text-feature_print">
							<p>By Jenny Shank, 12-11-07</p>
			
							<table width="25" align="right" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
