<a href="http://www.newwest.net/?URL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newwest.net%2Ftopic%2Farticle%2Fgood_grief_bob_cherrys_moving_serafina%2FC39%2FL39%2F">http://www.newwest.net/topic/article/good_grief_bob_cherrys_moving_serafina/C39/L39/</a><br />
<br />
And Stephen, thanks for the tip on a Utah book.  I look forward to checking out "Bargaining for Eden."  I promise Utah will be better represented here in 2008!</p>
		
